metadata.name: FAIROUZ #6
metadata.description: You don’t have to be Lebanese to know the name Fairouz. Fairouz is a living legend, one of the last singers from her era, still alive and performing. Fairuz is considered the musical icon of Lebanon and is popularly known as "the soul of Lebanon". The iconic singer, who quickly rose to prominence with her harmonic vocals, had the ability to unite entire generations of Arabs through decades of conflict with her music, resulting in the popular saying, " Lebanese People will disagree on everything, except Fairouz." Collect, Buy or Sell your Favorite NFT Fairouz Since only 150 NFTS will be created.
